{
  "stem": "3973.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 20.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I mean, we don't worry about the fact that we have not found any place to stay.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The next day, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my mother got dressed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She was wearing her best dress, I remember, a blue with white polka dots and lipstick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And she didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She went to the policeman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was 14 and really naive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, yes, I knew, and I didn't, this kind of a thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But when she left, there was a meadow outside of the hut.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I laid in the meadow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I didn't stay in the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "She left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I saw her going, but I didn't [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] say anything to her.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I was just lying there, maybe three or four hours.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That's at least my best recollection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this was a beautiful summer day, sort of a great day to be alive.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Looking at this later on, I always said to myself-- I kept some journals and did some writing about these things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I refer to this as the day I said goodbye to life, which is partly true, not quite.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The fact is that, you know, there were birds singing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I was lying in the grass.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And all the insects were buzzing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it was just a lovely day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I heard the voice of the kids playing in the background.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I felt very strongly that-- that I'm going to die.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "It was a terrible feeling, which I never allowed myself before to feel this way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Except in this case, it was intensified by the fact that my mother went to that policeman.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I was lying there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
